1. data base analysis

1-1. data base

CCLE(Cancer Cell Line Encyclopedia) CCLE project human cancer model panel . Genome pattern cell line integrative genomics . CCLE CCLE project data , 1100 cancer cell line genome data, access database .

1-2. data base

genome data Copy Number, mRNA expression (Affy), RPPA, RRBS, and mRNA expression (RNAseq), oncomap mutation, Pharmacological Profiling, hybrid capture sequencing . box plot, scatter plot, bubble map .

2. Introduction

ferroptosis lipid ROS , AIFM2 (apoptosis inducing factor mitochondria associated 2), GPX4 (glutathione peroxidase 4 encoding gene), SLC7A11 (cystein transport encoding gene) mutation . CCLE_RNAseq_genes_rpkm_20180929.gct.gz data cancer cell line site (organ) ferroptosis suppressing gene ( AIFM2, GPX4, SLC7A11) mRNA expression . mRNA expression site , site specific change . , data RPKM Reads Per Kilobase per Millions mapped reads normalized sequencing expression. Kilobase(=1000 base pair) reads gene mapping reads .
